<h1 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 25px;">Our Projects</h1>
<br />
<br />

 <div class="row">
     <div class="col-md-4">
         <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; margin-bottom:15px;">
             <img class="card-img-top" src="https://www.bradtguides.com/wp-content/uploads/wysiwyg/marketing/events/CCFphoto.png" alt="Card image cap">
             <div class="card-body">
                 <h5 class="card-title">The Cheetah Foundation</h5>
                 <p class="card-text">In efforts to fund research and conservation on wild cheetahs in Southern Africa.</p>
